<p>The way I deal with the spam messages is to hit ALT+O and turn them off.&nbsp;&nbsp;I also turn off all the pretty colors.  Dont need them. Too distractiing.  Being a good bard means staying focused at all times.   <br /> <br />Agreed. Your 3 or 4 most commonly used songs should be in the top hot key slots.  I always keep Selo's Accelerando in slot 4 unless I am indoors.  Then I use my best charm song - just in case I need an exit.</p>
