<p>I did not see a description of this hotkey, but it would seem the least problematic: <br /> <br />Melody <br /> <br />/melody #.#.#.# <br /> <br /> <br />In place of the # of course is your song slot number.&nbsp;&nbsp;If it misses a note just hit the hotkey again.  Allows greater freedom to melee and with the new bandolier for weapons/instruments and a hotkey for them, makes for much smoother enjoyable playing :) <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Sun Jul 24 22:23:02 2005 by ellyra</span></i></p>
